        '<ul>\n' +
        '<li><strong>transformers</strong> : 提供了可以轻松地下载并且训练先进的预训练模型的 API 和工具。</li>\n' +
        '<li><strong>unsloth</strong> : 量化训练，减少显存消耗。</li>\n' +
        '<li><strong>wandb</strong> : 可视化训练过程</li>\n' +
        '</ul>\n' +
        '<pre class="astro-code catppuccin-frappe" style="background-color:#303446;color:#c6d0f5; overflow-x: auto;" tabindex="0" data-language="python"><code><span class="line"><span style="color:#81C8BE">%</span><span style="color:#C6D0F5">pip install transformers unsloth wandb datasets accelerate</span></span></code></pre>\n' +
        '<pre class="astro-code catppuccin-frappe" style="background-color:#303446;color:#c6d0f5; overflow-x: auto;" tabindex="0" data-language="python"><code><span class="line"><span style="color:#CA9EE6">from</span><span style="color:#C6D0F5"> datasets </span><span style="color:#CA9EE6">import</span><span style="color:#C6D0F5"> load_dataset</span></span>\n' +
